        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> Seriously, why even have a zone in the game that is so utterly fucking hostile to players that it's nearly empty?  </P><P>I mean, you can huddle around the temple, or the pond with the sun revs, but travelling through this zone is treacherous as hell, and trying to work the walls / spawns is nuts.</P><P>You can't walk 20 seconds without setting off a goddamn trap in this zone.  Why?  Because dr00ds were able to use upheavel or whatever to kill 20 mobs at a time.  Instead of fixing the spell, or fixing the class, the zone was made so hostile to prevent this, that the rest of the player base gets fucked in the process.</P><P>How about making upheavel work on 4 mobs, or a small radius or something, anything.  But for christ sake, fix this zone.  I mean, if I designed this zone (and the layout, graphics are nice) I would cry in my coffee to see how fucked up it is now.  Have some pride in your product, Verant.  </P><P>If the coders who came up with this horse shit were standing behind the president of Sony Entertainment who was trying to play the game, in this zone, in front of them, would they be proud of their work?  I bet not.</P><P>This is one of my favorite zones in the game due to the ambience, graphics and layout.  But the traps every 5 step bullshit needs to be fixed, man.  How you can expect your customers to enjoy themselves in such a player punishing environment is beyond me.</P><P>Please fix this zone.</P><P><BR><img src="http://www.bloodofro.com/members/gallery_img/sihk.jpg" border=0><BR><a href="http://www.bloodofro.com" target="_blank">http://www.bloodofro.com</a><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=149939" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=149939</a></font></td>

